trans-unit.source: Represents the base class for classes that perform operations on two operands, such as <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Plus" />, <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Equality" />, and <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Relational" />.
trans-unit.target: Stellt die Basisklasse für Klassen dar, die Operationen mit zwei Operanden ausführen, z. B. <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Plus" />, <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Equality" /> und <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.Relational" />.

trans-unit.source: This class belongs to the abstract syntax tree category.
trans-unit.target: Diese Klasse gehört zur Kategorie für abstrakte Syntaxstrukturen.

trans-unit.source: The data type of the first operand.
The data type of the second operand.
Determines the best method to call based on the operation that is requested and the data types of the operands.
trans-unit.target: Bestimmt die beste Aufrufmethode anhand der angeforderten Operation und des Datentyps der Operanden.

trans-unit.source: The recommended method to call on the operands.
trans-unit.target: Die zum Aufrufen der Operanden empfohlene Methode.

trans-unit.source: Represents the first operand of the operation.
trans-unit.target: Stellt den ersten Operanden der Operation dar.

trans-unit.source: Represents the second operand of the operation.
trans-unit.target: Stellt den zweiten Operanden der Operation dar.

trans-unit.source: Represents the operation that is actually performed.
trans-unit.target: Stellt die tatsächlich ausgeführte Operation dar.

trans-unit.source: Represents the operation that is requested.
One of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.JScript.JSToken" /> enumeration values.
Represents the data type of the first operand of the operation.
trans-unit.target: Stellt den Datentyp des ersten Operanden der Operation dar.

trans-unit.source: Represents the data type of the second operand of the operation.
trans-unit.target: Stellt den Datentyp des zweiten Operanden der Operation dar.
